abstract: LIBERTY, Me., Oct. 7.--Ambrose Daggett, a young man working on the farm of David Greely, this evening shot Ella, a young daughter of Greely, through the neck, causing instant death. abstract: Quite a novel and ingenious device is that adopted by the Democrats in some of the southwestern counties of Virginia. abstract: MILWAUKEE, Oct. 13.--Four wholesale houses have been entered by burglars lately--two last night and the safes were cracked by professional blowers. abstract: PLYMOUTH, Mass., Oct. 24.--James Gilmore, who set fire to the Bridgewater Work-house some month ago, causing its destruction, was sentenced this afternoon to 20 years in the State prison.
